data.title: Industrial Cat 6A Shielded 600 V Patch Cord, 3m, TL
data.text:
The IndustrialNet Cat 6A Shielded Patch Cord is constructed of industrial grade, 26 AWG, SF/UTP, twisted pair, stranded, CMR cable with industrial bulkhead modular plugs with black strain relief boots. It is designed to support high-flex applications and is rated for 600 V panel or on-machine applications where space is shared with high voltage power cables. The patch cord is 3 meters in length and teal.

Application

(1) 10BASE-T (Ethernet)(2) 100BASE-T (Fast Ethernet)(3) 1000BASE-T (Gigabit Ethernet)(4) Industrial Ethernet(5) Ethernet/IP(6) Control Panel deployments featuring power source voltages(7) Uplinks featuring gigabit data transmission from the control panel
